<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#D0BC90">Originally posted by knightwolf78753 on 10-27-2002 01:18 AM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=20 COLS=75 WRAP="VIRTUAL">ok first off I got through the catacombs just fine. I have just started the game over maybe thinking my stats were messed up for a warrior. Still im having the same problems. like right now im level 10 or so and im at the abby trying to kill every thing there. Now Ive gotten through most of the stuff with no problems. I just beat the conjure. Now the thing thats kicking my butt and have no idea how to beat is the Steal Guards I think there called. now you talk about healing but correct me if im wrong but having heal potions to save your butt from dying is part of the game. Now normally i would use the old Diablo trick were  port to town and get a heal and then port back and contuinue fighting but when you do this mob is full healed to. Now running out of health potions and not using the Diablo 2 tactic presents a sort of a problem. O and running some times doesnt do a damn bit of good cause they will still chase you down and drive there sword through your heart. 
 Now as far as saving its not that I dont have a problem saving the problem is the fact that when I get caught up in to the game I forget to save now sense I dont know what lurks around every corner and how hard the mob is I cant always anticapate whats coming. It really sucks losing 30 min worth of work heck even 15 min worth of work. Especially if you just got done moving through a whole lot of nastys that were some what of a challange. 
 Now you talk about potions and mixing them well seeing how I dont know how to do that and the game doesnt tell you how I didnt know about it and I cant read the larian minds as far as what they put in the game. 
 To me the game is off balance as far as save and healing and gold is concerened. Im flat broke right now with heal potions that suck cause of how high my con is. Yes normally there ok but when I have a big bad guy that can kill me in 4 or 5 hits those potions dont do squat. 
 O and dont tell me this game is not like Diablo cause its plays so much like it that it almost seems like diablo 2. I played Diablo 2 for almost sense it came out. I have yet to come accross an RPG that could match Diablo 2 this game has come close to being as good as Diablo 2 but not totally.</TEXTAREA>
</td></tr>
